title: Does Lana Del Rey Love Coffee?: BuzzFeed Investigates
text:

Premiere / Premiere/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569485 4. September 5, 2015: After a relatively tame and coffee-free 2014, Lana makes her first 2015 public appearance with her man and her coffee. View this image ›
Stoianov / Stoianov/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569477 5. February 2, 2016: In the early days of 2016, Lana is back on the coffee bandwagon. View this image ›
Premiere / Premiere/Stoianov/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569483 6. March 27, 2016: Lana has a big coffee. 10569493 7. April 1, 2016: Lana has another coffee. View this image ›
Cpr / CPR/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569486 8. April 10, 2016: Lana has a coffee and a newspaper. View this image ›
Bruce / Bruce/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569491 9. August 22, 2016: Lana leaves a “Western Bagel” location with not one or two BUT three coffees. Two hot and one iced. View this image ›
Bruce / Bruce/Javiles/CPR/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569480 10. !!! View this image ›
Bruce / Bruce/Javiles/CPR/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569567 11. She could barely open the door! View this image ›
Bruce / Bruce/Javiles/CPR/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569568 12. August 22, 2016: After her earlier three coffee binge, Lana is spotted chatting with an older gentleman and his dog at, yup, you guessed it, a coffee shop! View this image ›
Cpr / CPR/Bruce/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569488 13. August 29, 2016: Lana delicately holds a small coffee. View this image ›
Osvaldo / Osvaldo/Eagle Eye/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569484 14. The morning of October 3, 2016: Lana has a big coffee. View this image ›
Bruce / Bruce/4CRNS/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569489 15. Later that day on October 3, 2016: Lana has a teeny tiny coffee. View this image ›
Bruce / Bruce/4CRNS/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569479 16. December 19, 2016: Lana has two coffees. View this image ›
Bruce / Bruce/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569569 17. Double trouble! View this image ›
Bruce / Bruce/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569492 18. February 1st, 2017: She’s back to only one coffee. View this image ›
Javiles / Javiles/FAMEFLYNET PICTURES ID: 10569494 19. So, what does it all mean? Well, my best guess is that Lana Del Rey probably likes coffee. ID: 10570957 20. Thank you for the last two minutes of your life. View this image ›
